    # "We follow the trail ahead, the scent of cooking food and campfire drifting through the trees, until I spot a light up ahead, and a woman sitting next to the fire."
    "我们沿着前方的足迹前行，烹饪食物和篝火的香气在树林间飘荡，直到我看到前方有灯光，还有一位坐在火堆旁的女子。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:72
translate chinese u19a2s11_0c6f7575:

    # "I follow the trail ahead, the scent of cooking food and campfire drifting through the trees, until I spot a light up ahead, and a woman sitting next to the fire."
