    # fd "Hey there! Are ya hungry? I think I have enough food here to share."
    fd "嗨！你饿了吗？我觉得我这儿的食物足够分你一些。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:77
translate chinese u19a2s11_eeef8efd:

    # fd "Wait, how did you know my name?"
    fd "等等，你怎么知道我的名字？"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:78
translate chinese u19a2s11_71ff9b4d:

    # pc "Well that's a long story."
    pc "这个嘛，说来话长。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:79
translate chinese u19a2s11_29a1c8a6:

    # fd "Sit and tell me while I finish up dinner then."
    fd "那你坐下，等我把晚饭做好了再跟我说吧。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:114
translate chinese u19a2s11_73c2e02d:

    # "I sit and try to explain to her about the other world, the bracelet, and the Ice Queen."
    "我坐下来，试图向她解释那个异世界、手镯以及冰雪女王的事。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:115
translate chinese u19a2s11_af2b3633:

    # "She mostly just nods and smiles."
    "她大多只是点头微笑。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:121
translate chinese u19a2s11_f88e1ab3:

    # fd "That's a crazy story, but not the craziest I've heard."
    fd "这故事真离奇，不过倒不是我听过的最离奇的。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:122
translate chinese u19a2s11_d866ad57:

    # fd "Well, if you're going to face the Ice Queen, you're likely going to die."
    fd "呃，如果你要去面对冰雪女王，恐怕是死定了。"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act2/act2scene11.rpy:123
translate chinese u19a2s11_6c332b14:

    # fd "And if you're going to die tomorrow, might as well party tonight, I say."
    fd "既然明天就要死了，那今晚不如好好狂欢一番，我说。"

